    "description": "鲨币派对是一款独具风格的多人联机派对游戏。游戏中玩家们将在多种形式的地图中，寻找地图中的鲨币并收集它们，将鲨币交给鲨鱼王来获取鲨鱼王的声望，最终获得最多鲨鱼王的声望的小队/个人将成为比赛的冠军。<br>在游戏中，你可以扮演多种具有不同能力的角色，有的角色更擅长在环境中快速灵活地移动，有的则更偏重攻击其他角色。组成小队并指定战术来合作取胜吧。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >8张可游玩地图，更多地图将持续推出</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/a750e0c7ff8258de8b5030f41b846f03.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=334 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/8b58e76cacd7e6e44e9119591f487089.poster.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/8b58e76cacd7e6e44e9119591f487089.webm?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/8b58e76cacd7e6e44e9119591f487089.mp4?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>骑上飞龙进行火球轰炸!或者飞到高空！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cb07ae182a92cf8dbc0ced7316f584b7.poster.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cb07ae182a92cf8dbc0ced7316f584b7.webm?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cb07ae182a92cf8dbc0ced7316f584b7.mp4?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在游玩过程中不断解锁新角色，现有11个可选角色，每个角色都有多种可选的技能变种</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/d38a84667d9b620d4a13eb16ea79ab12.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=342 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每个角色的能力都独特而有趣，机动性或者破坏性由你选择！</h2></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/3e42eddd385d97a4c13efb9360e2badd.poster.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/3e42eddd385d97a4c13efb9360e2badd.webm?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/3e42eddd385d97a4c13efb9360e2badd.mp4?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cd1c6d406580967b6ecbc1156e48f26f.poster.avif?t=1723432322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cd1c6d406580967b6ecbc1156e48f26f.webm?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027630/extras/cd1c6d406580967b6ecbc1156e48f26f.mp4?t=1723432322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
